description:
CollectorConfig is the HCL-level shape of a `collector "http" "<id>" { ... }` block.

    collector "http" "github" {
      base_url = "https://api.github.com"
      timeout  = 30
      headers = {
        X-GitHub-Api-Version = "2022-11-28"
      }
      auth "basic" {
        username = env.GITHUB_USER
        password = env.GITHUB_TOKEN
      }
    }
